Name: Jumps
About the game: Jumps is a fast paced first person platformer, the aim of the game is to finish each world in under a certain amount of time, you have a limited amount of times you can jump for each level too. Jumps has 6 unique worlds to jump through, 10 levels in each. Each world introduces exciting new game mechanics to figure out and master, including trampolines, cannons, rocket jumping and more!
